
 * do not care too much about performance at the beginning of your project,
 it will be ok to take care of it later on,

 * create a basic architecture plan for a new feature on the piece of paper,

 * start from the high part of your system and then you will see what you really need
 - start from client need

 eg. the same situation is with woman. if she is nice from first look, if first impression
 is ok, then you probably won't be considering if she earns a lot of money straight away.

